# Ollama Local Model Configuration

This directory contains a generated Modelfile for local development.

Recommended commands:

```bash
ollama create {{ variables.project_name | lower }}-agent -f .ollama/Modelfile
ollama run {{ variables.project_name | lower }}-agent
```

Base URL for local tools:

```text
{{ model.base_url | default("http://localhost:11434") }}
```
